@startuml
title 時序圖：每幀更新

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam wrapWidth 220
skinparam maxMessageSize 220

participant "Godot Input System" as Input
participant "Camera2D\n:CameraController" as Camera2D
participant "Main\n:Node2D" as Main
participant "ParallaxManager\n:ParallaxLayerController" as ParallaxManager
participant "FocusValue / StatusValue / LayerValue\n:Label" as HudLabels

loop every frame
  Camera2D -> Input : `get_axis(left, right)`\n讀取左右移動輸入
  Camera2D -> Camera2D : `_process(delta)`\n執行每幀相機更新
  Camera2D -> Camera2D : update horizontal position\n更新水平位置

  Main -> Main : `_process(delta)`\n執行每幀主流程
  Main -> Main : `_update_hud()`\n更新 HUD 內容
  Main -> ParallaxManager : `get_offset_mode_name()`\n查詢 offset 模式
  Main -> ParallaxManager : `get_repeat_mode_name()`\n查詢 repeat 模式
  Main -> ParallaxManager : `get_layer_lines()`\n查詢圖層摘要
  Main -> HudLabels : refresh camera/mode/layer text\n刷新 HUD 文字
end

note right of Main
每幀更新重點：
- 相機移動
- HUD 同步
end note

@enduml
